{"tid":2232293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"談彭亮廷大判官判管有六角匙的18歲男生入更生中心","createTime":"2020-10-06T09:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T01:14:37.000Z","uid":26770,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"879d874a6887c3ab65b3c5e0e49d14cc5484f7f7","tid":2232293,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:36:35.000Z","msg":"單案案情<br />\n純粹係藏有六角匙係身,司法迫害受害者咩都無做過<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2232135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2232135</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201709/27/P2017092700425.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201709%2F27%2FP2017092700425.htm&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKKnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=a53b24c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201709/27/P2017092700425.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">撈doj 3年都升唔到<br />\n2005-2017私人執業<br />\n私人市場撈12年都起唔到<br />\n<br />\n轉黨委法官搏升主任mag仔袋十萬糧<br />\nmag court一直係法律界綜援,無底線又無料的人排隊出糧</span><br />\n<br />\n<del>彭亮廷<br />\n<br />\n  彭亮廷於一九七七年在香港出生。二○○○年及二○○一年在香港大學分別取得法學學士學位及法學專業證書。二○○一年在香港獲大律師資格。二○○二年至二○○五年期間加入政府律政司出任政府律師。二○○五年起私人執業。</del>"},{"pid":"07beee26045d071b5edbe22c5e1b329b163de15d","tid":2232293,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:38:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f24d12de510a8cacc20845f3cb0e81b0efd07f","tid":2232293,"uid":26770,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:39:36.000Z","msg":"有一定水平的老鬼打單誹謗都幾萬幾萬上<br />\n以此高齡去咬法律界綜援根本就係法律界的忠誠勇毅"},{"pid":"75f6189479e9d5a50c1954eae9ea032b63f307e4","tid":2232293,"uid":112081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5fca00922b1a80bedd24f02bdd5840d266aa85","tid":2232293,"uid":219128,"like":0,"dis