ad/2177067/page/1</a><br />\n特別係dq私人檢控幫警暴護航的副專員蕭啟業"},{"pid":"2fff4d95c5ee3bfb8dfa6e9ed8226eab5e72fdfe","tid":2232293,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:39:52.000Z","msg":"n單幾個警魔口供前後完全矛盾<br />\n奶共法院次次照屈警暴受害人坐監,仲講咩因為完全矛盾所以可信<br />\n<br />\n而大家見所謂法劣界次次就<strong>spin去不評論案件</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">大陸屍會咪姐係法治界荷蘭叻<br />\n我唔知,我唔信,我見唔到所以司法迫害不存在</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xXWg2Bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxXWg2Bb.jpg&h=e0a113cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0b6d89a03f40200482306f9380042bc3cf60e9e","tid":2232293,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:44:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51085a49f6959d38503c704c64a508bc1738ccfa","tid":2232293,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:46:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"177e4ec6fa4e37cd1f63fbb82b5e71f8e9e88f45","tid":2232293,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:47:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4043ee48ab3572ba790b34aca071abf3737c333d","tid":2232293,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:14:37.000Z","msg":"智利警推示威者落樓單野,政府立即拉人<br />\n---------<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">但....香港模式</span><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">法官:我簽搜查令迫死荃灣警局輪姦案受害人先,受害人釘左咪無CASE<br />\n轉頭個女就升主任MAG仔袋十萬糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大律師公會:你班賤民屌我對司法迫害扮盲都無用,我咪9UP不評論個別案件</span></span>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"4043ee48ab3572ba790b34aca071abf3737c333d","tid":2232293,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:14:3